<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>California Residential Purchase Agreement and Joint Escrow Instructions</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 10pt;
            line-height: 1.3;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #000;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #000;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 14pt;
            margin: 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .header .subtitle {
            font-size: 10pt;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            page-break-inside: avoid;
        }
        .section-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            font-size: 11pt;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            padding: 3px 5px;
        }
        .field-group {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .field-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            display: inline-block;
            min-width: 150px;
        }
        .field-value {
            display: inline-block;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
            min-width: 200px;
            padding: 0 5px;
        }
        .checkbox {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 12px;
            height: 12px;
            border: 1px solid #000;
            margin-right: 5px;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }
        .checkbox.checked::after {
            content: "✓";
            display: block;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 12px;
        }
        .terms {
            font-size: 9pt;
            margin-top: 10px;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        .signature-section {
            margin-top: 30px;
            border-top: 2px solid #000;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }
        .signature-line {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 250px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .signature-label {
            font-size: 9pt;
            color: #666;
        }
        .page-break {
            page-break-after: always;
        }
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        table td {
            padding: 5px;
            vertical-align: top;
        }
        .warning-box {
            border: 2px solid #000;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>CALIFORNIA RESIDENTIAL PURCHASE AGREEMENT AND JOINT ESCROW INSTRUCTIONS</h1>
        <div class="subtitle">(C.A.R. Form RPA-CA, Revised 12/23)</div>
        <div class="subtitle">For use by Realtors® only</div>
    </div>

    <div class="warning-box">
        THIS IS MORE THAN A RECEIPT FOR MONEY. IT IS INTENDED TO BE A LEGALLY BINDING CONTRACT. READ IT CAREFULLY.
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">1. OFFER</div>
        <div class="field-group">
            <span class="field-label">A. THIS IS AN OFFER FROM</span>
            <span class="field-value">{{buyerName}}</span>
            <span>("Buyer")</span>
        </div>
        <div class="field-group">
            <span class="field-label">B. THE REAL PROPERTY TO BE ACQUIRED</span>
            <span class="field-value">{{propertyAddress}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="field-group">
            <span class="field-label">City</span>
            <span class="field-value">{{propertyCity}}</span>
            <span class="field-label">County</span>
            <span class="field-value">{{propertyCounty}}</span>
            <span class="field-label">CA Zip Code</span>
            <span class="field-value">{{propertyZip}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="field-group">
            <span class="field-label">Assessor's Parcel No.</span>
            <span class="field-value">{{assessorParcelNumber}}</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">2. AGENCY RELATIONSHIPS</div>
        <table>
            <tr>
                <td width="50%">
                    <div class="field-group">
                        <span class="field-label">Listing Agent</span>
                        <span class="field-value">{{listingAgentName}}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="field-group">
                        <span class="field-label">DRE Lic. #</span>
                        <span class="field-value">{{listingAgentLicense}}</span>
                    </div>
                </td>
                <td width="50%">
                    <div class="field-group">
                        <span class="field-label">Selling Agent</span>
                        <span class="field-value">{{sellingAgentName}}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="field-group">
                        <span class="field-label">DRE Lic. #</span>
                        <span class="field-value">{{sellingAgentLicense}}</span>
                    </div>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">3. PURCHASE PRICE AND FINANCING</div>
        <div class="field-group">
            <span class="field-label">A. Offered Purchase Price</span>
            <span class="field-value">${{formatCurrency purchasePrice}}</span>
        </div>
        
        <div style="margin-left: 20px;">
            <div class="field-group">
                <span class="field-label">B. Initial Deposit</span>
                <span class="field-value">${{formatCurrency initialDeposit}}</span>
                <span>to be deposited within {{depositDays}} business days after acceptance</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="field-group">
                <span class="field-label">C. Increased Deposit</span>
                <span class="field-value">${{formatCurrency increasedDeposit}}</span>
                <span>to be deposited within {{increasedDepositDays}} days after acceptance</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="field-group">
                <span class="field-label">D. Down Payment</span>
                <span class="field-value">${{formatCurrency downPayment}}</span>
                <span>({{downPaymentPercent}}% of purchase price)</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="field-group">
                <span class="field-label">E. Loan Amount</span>
                <span class="field-value">${{formatCurrency loanAmount}}</span>
                <div style="margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 5px;">
                    <div class="checkbox {{#if isConventional}}checked{{/if}}"></div> Conventional
                    <div class="checkbox {{#if isFHA}}checked{{/if}}"></div> FHA
                    <div class="checkbox {{#if isVA}}checked{{/if}}"></div> VA
                    <div class="checkbox {{#if isOther}}checked{{/if}}"></div> Other: <span class="field-value">{{loanOther}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">4. CLOSING AND OCCUPANCY</div>
        <div class="field-group">
            <span class="field-label">A. Close of Escrow</span>
            <span class="field-value">{{closingDate}}</span>
            <span>or {{closingDaysAfterAcceptance}} days after acceptance</span>
        </div>
        <div class="field-group">
            <span class="field-label">B. Buyer Occupancy</span>
            <div style="margin-left: 20px;">
                <div><div class="checkbox {{#if occupancyAtClose}}checked{{/if}}"></div> At Close of Escrow</div>
                <div><div class="checkbox {{#if occupancyNotLater}}checked{{/if}}"></div> No later than <span class="field-value">{{occupancyDays}}</span> days after Close of Escrow</div>
                <div><div class="checkbox {{#if occupancyTBD}}checked{{/if}}"></div> To Be Determined per attached Occupancy Agreement</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">5. ALLOCATION OF COSTS</div>
        <table>
            <tr>
                <td><strong>INSPECTION, REPORTS AND CERTIFICATES</strong></td>
                <td width="80px" align="center"><strong>BUYER</strong></td>
                <td width="80px" align="center"><strong>SELLER</strong></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Wood Destroying Pest Inspection</td>
                <td align="center"><div class="checkbox {{#if pestInspectionBuyer}}checked{{/if}}"></div></td>
                <td align="center"><div class="checkbox {{#if pestInspectionSeller}}checked{{/if}}"></div></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Property Inspection</td>
                <td align="center"><div class="checkbox {{#if propertyInspectionBuyer}}checked{{/if}}"></div></td>
                <td align="center"><div class="checkbox {{#if propertyInspectionSeller}}checked{{/if}}"></div></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Home Warranty Plan</td>
                <td align="center"><div class="checkbox {{#if homeWarrantyBuyer}}checked{{/if}}"></div></td>
                <td align="center"><div class="checkbox {{#if homeWarrantySeller}}checked{{/if}}"></div></td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">6. STATUTORY AND OTHER DISCLOSURES</div>
        <div class="terms">
            <p>Within the time specified in paragraph 14A, Seller shall provide Buyer with all required statutory disclosures including:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Real Estate Transfer Disclosure Statement (TDS)</li>
                <li>Natural Hazard Disclosure Statement (NHD)</li>
                <li>Lead-Based Paint Disclosure (if applicable)</li>
                <li>Earthquake Guides (if applicable)</li>
                <li>Environmental Hazards Booklet</li>
                <li>Database Disclosure (Megan's Law)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">7. CONTINGENCIES</div>
        <div class="field-group">
            <strong>A. LOAN CONTINGENCY:</strong> Buyer shall act diligently and in good faith to obtain the loan(s) specified above.
        </div>
        <div class="field-group">
            <strong>B. APPRAISAL CONTINGENCY:</strong> This Agreement is contingent upon the Property appraising at no less than the purchase price.
        </div>
        <div class="field-group">
            <strong>C. INVESTIGATION CONTINGENCY:</strong> Buyer's obligation is contingent upon Buyer's investigation and approval of the Property.
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="page-break"></div>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">8. ITEMS INCLUDED AND EXCLUDED</div>
        <div class="field-group">
            <strong>A. INCLUDED:</strong> All existing fixtures and fittings that are attached to the Property including:
            <div style="margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 5px;">
                {{#if includeAppliances}}<div class="checkbox checked"></div> Appliances: {{appliances}}<br>{{/if}}
                {{#if includeFixtures}}<div class="checkbox checked"></div> Light fixtures, window coverings<br>{{/if}}
                {{#if includeOther}}<div class="checkbox checked"></div> Other: {{includedOther}}<br>{{/if}}
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="field-group">
            <strong>B. EXCLUDED:</strong> {{excluded}}
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">9. BUYER'S INVESTIGATION OF PROPERTY</div>
        <div class="terms">
            Buyer shall have {{inspectionDays}} days after acceptance to complete all investigations and review all disclosures, reports, and other applicable information. Buyer may cancel this Agreement based on any dissatisfaction with the condition of the Property by providing written notice to Seller within this time period.
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">10. REPAIRS</div>
        <div class="field-group">
            <div class="checkbox {{#if noRepairs}}checked{{/if}}"></div> Seller shall make no repairs
        </div>
        <div class="field-group">
            <div class="checkbox {{#if hasRepairs}}checked{{/if}}"></div> Seller shall complete the following repairs prior to Close of Escrow:
            <div style="margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 5px;">
                {{repairs}}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">11. FINAL VERIFICATION OF CONDITION</div>
        <div class="terms">
            Buyer shall have the right to make a final inspection of the Property within {{finalWalkDays}} days prior to Close of Escrow to confirm: (i) the Property is maintained in substantially the same condition as on the date of Acceptance; (ii) all Seller repairs have been completed; and (iii) Seller has complied with other obligations under this Agreement.
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">12. PRORATIONS</div>
        <div class="terms">
            Property taxes, HOA dues, rents, and other expenses of the Property shall be prorated as of Close of Escrow. Any supplemental tax bills shall be handled as follows: (i) for periods after Close of Escrow, Buyer shall pay; (ii) for periods prior to Close of Escrow, Seller shall pay.
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">13. TITLE AND VESTING</div>
        <div class="field-group">
            <span class="field-label">Title to vest in:</span>
            <span class="field-value">{{vestingName}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="field-group">
            <span class="field-label">Manner of taking title:</span>
            <span class="field-value">{{vestingType}}</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">14. TIME PERIODS</div>
        <table>
            <tr>
                <td>A. Seller to provide disclosures:</td>
                <td width="100px"><span class="field-value">{{disclosureDays}}</span> days</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>B. Buyer investigation/contingency period:</td>
                <td><span class="field-value">{{contingencyDays}}</span> days</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>C. Loan contingency removal:</td>
                <td><span class="field-value">{{loanContingencyDays}}</span> days</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>D. Appraisal contingency removal:</td>
                <td><span class="field-value">{{appraisalContingencyDays}}</span> days</td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>

    <div class="signature-section">
        <div class="section-title">BUYER SIGNATURE</div>
        <table width="100%">
            <tr>
                <td width="50%">
                    <div class="signature-line"></div>
                    <div class="signature-label">Buyer Signature</div>
                    <div class="field-group">
                        <span class="field-label">Print Name:</span>
                        <span class="field-value">{{buyerName}}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="field-group">
                        <span class="field-label">Date:</span>
                        <span class="field-value">{{buyerSignatureDate}}</span>
                    </div>
                </td>
                <td width="50%">
                    {{#if buyerName2}}
                    <div class="signature-line"></div>
                    <div class="signature-label">Buyer Signature</div>
                    <div class="field-group">
                        <span class="field-label">Print Name:</span>
                        <span class="field-value">{{buyerName2}}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="field-group">
                        <span class="field-label">Date:</span>
                        <span class="field-value">{{buyerSignatureDate2}}</span>
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>

    <div class="page-break"></div>

    <div class="signature-section">
        <div class="section-title">SELLER ACCEPTANCE</div>
        <div class="terms">
            Seller accepts the above offer and agrees to sell the Property on the above terms and conditions.
        </div>
        <table width="100%" style="margin-top: 20px;">
            <tr>
                <td width="50%">
                    <div class="signature-line"></div>
                    <div class="signature-label">Seller Signature</div>
                    <div class="field-group">
                        <span class="field-label">Print Name:</span>
                        <span class="field-value">{{sellerName}}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="field-group">
                        <span class="field-label">Date:</span>
                        <span class="field-value">{{sellerSignatureDate}}</span>
                    </div>
                </td>
                <td width="50%">
                    {{#if sellerName2}}
                    <div class="signature-line"></div>
                    <div class="signature-label">Seller Signature</div>
                    <div class="field-group">
                        <span class="field-label">Print Name:</span>
                        <span class="field-value">{{sellerName2}}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="field-group">
                        <span class="field-label">Date:</span>
                        <span class="field-value">{{sellerSignatureDate2}}</span>
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>

    <div class="section" style="margin-top: 40px;">
        <div class="section-title">REAL ESTATE BROKER INFORMATION</div>
        <table width="100%">
            <tr>
                <td width="50%">
                    <strong>Listing Broker:</strong><br>
                    <div class="field-value">{{listingBrokerName}}</div><br>
                    DRE Lic. #: <span class="field-value">{{listingBrokerLicense}}</span><br>
                    By: <span class="field-value">{{listingAgentName}}</span>
                </td>
                <td width="50%">
                    <strong>Selling Broker:</strong><br>
                    <div class="field-value">{{sellingBrokerName}}</div><br>
                    DRE Lic. #: <span class="field-value">{{sellingBrokerLicense}}</span><br>
                    By: <span class="field-value">{{sellingAgentName}}</span>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>

    <div class="terms" style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 8pt;">
        <p><strong>THIS FORM HAS BEEN APPROVED BY THE CALIFORNIA ASSOCIATION OF REALTORS® (C.A.R.).</strong></p>
        <p>NO REPRESENTATION IS MADE AS TO THE LEGAL VALIDITY OR ACCURACY OF ANY PROVISION IN ANY SPECIFIC TRANSACTION. A REAL ESTATE BROKER IS THE PERSON QUALIFIED TO ADVISE ON REAL ESTATE TRANSACTIONS. IF YOU DESIRE LEGAL OR TAX ADVICE, CONSULT AN APPROPRIATE PROFESSIONAL.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>